<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_2b616198-57f3-4671-945e-9e1c0c192864" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="NSW"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/></meta><sptc>9.4.3</sptc><title id="_5312139a-65f0-4a22-9cc7-5b0e13d26a15">Construction of walls</title><archive-num>2019: NSW 1.1.3</archive-num><subclause id="_31e05027-4676-4f77-aaa5-af8f377878cf" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_25019175-4359-4d74-8ef6-e4bf58938f16">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A wall <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_25b038aa-bfbb-4ca5-b60f-02d981bb91cf" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/6999_0.8.0.xml#_85a5105f-9a1b-419e-89b9-17ced1649cae" id="_72a35c99-a75c-4fc1-a411-e6178efd4892" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">NSW 9.4.1(2)</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/6999_0.8.0.xml#_618dd0d5-1137-446c-8382-aec8280caa5c" id="_7de0c0b4-e6e3-424d-b721-61372fd0d6f3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">NSW 9.4.1(3)(a)</xref> must—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_81f3ac14-c575-4215-91a2-5f418e8de884">have an FRL of not less than 30/30/30 when tested from the non-associated <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1414_4.2.0.xml#_230a3a0f-1539-4b9d-9a2d-8edf732e59dd" id="_cbd38bde-f492-47ef-aff9-3ec0b19ff828" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">private garage</xref> side; or</li><li id="_500ff20e-f1fe-457e-b620-3ed0683c38ce">be of masonry construction not less than 90 mm thick.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_d94de3b2-f728-41fe-befc-07236e637cbc" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_268ef35e-da7f-4139-b009-85e34870f8e1">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>A wall subject to (1) must—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_4c87eeca-12ce-4f96-b634-433b3958821c">commence at the footings or ground slab; and</li><li id="_81b0ddfc-ad9a-4b76-aa1a-ab41c0b3a266">extend to the underside of a floor complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/7000_0.7.0.xml#_e9f2be4a-924e-4658-959d-befa24825186" id="_6e649ae2-0f0c-4a21-8dee-e74932ef1d02" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">NSW 9.4.2</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_d78d8e59-f2fb-4a44-86d5-3ad1609d7b41" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_1536fbbb-847d-47aa-832b-7953dbb532bc">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>A wall referred to in (1)(a), if of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1359_0.4.0.xml#_2cf43983-ddc7-4b7f-b16e-2d3ed619886e" id="_ab833c2f-abb6-4c98-8890-1377db6e39f3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">lightweight construction</xref> must be tested in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/141#_e5ff9fe3-2084-4425-9e49-c8d7f5717cda" id="_cc415261-57ac-4c90-a6f1-5dd6ea99ec32" publishing-id="vol1" referencetype="Text" scope="external" synctargettext="false" type="specification">Specification 6</xref> of Volume One.</p></subclause><subclause id="_0c476ce7-76fe-4df9-b2b8-0621e2627878" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_b866919a-875f-41d0-bd68-fe073f794815">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>Where a service passes through a wall referred to in (1), the penetration must not reduce the performance of the wall.</p></subclause><subclause id="_9797c188-9413-414d-b58e-974ce7052095" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_14ad1d3e-46a6-4f42-89e0-928782932415">SubClause</title><num>5</num><p>A wall <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_96e2e906-3ef2-4b11-b97e-f8051709f920" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/6999_0.8.0.xml#_85a5105f-9a1b-419e-89b9-17ced1649cae" id="_a61dae00-e5d0-4a29-bb5a-5e5805936f7c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">NSW 9.4.1(2)</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/6999_0.8.0.xml#_618dd0d5-1137-446c-8382-aec8280caa5c" id="_9b67a6c7-73e2-4004-82e6-bc98e3058ad0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">NSW 9.4.1(3)(a)</xref> need not comply with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1856_1.6.0.xml#_0a5b3109-6525-4631-b8b7-3e798f8ebe96" id="_09278501-cc86-4561-84af-e2e416dc8d79" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">9.3.1</xref>.</p></subclause></clause>